{"id":34994,"date":"2024-01-12T08:24:00","date_gmt":"2022-06-12T02:54:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=34994"},"modified":"2023-03-31T15:21:47","modified_gmt":"2023-03-31T09:51:47","slug":"tufted-sofa-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/tufted-sofa-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"Trend Alert: 9 Tufted Sofa Designs And Why Your Home Needs One Now"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Tufted sofa designs are trending on every country\u2019s decor scene. Here\u2019s how to make them work for you.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tufted sofas are the rage with modern homeowners. Every <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/\">home decor<\/a> and furniture shop is displaying these beauties to the hilt. What is the reason for their ubiquitous popularity? Many, it would seem.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tufted sofas look timeless yet trendy. Without demanding the big bucks that most modern furniture items do, the tufted sofa design transforms a simple couch into eye candy in the living room. This furniture style finds its niche in every decade. It is as much at home in a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/vintage-living-room\/\">vintage living room<\/a> as in a mid-century or modern drawing room.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>But what is a tufted sofa? It is any couch that uses upholstered buttons on its surface to create interesting patterns. Diamond, biscuit and channel tufting designs are some of the patterns that are most in vogue. Take a look at some of our favourite tufted sofas along with tips on how you can style one in your own home.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Vintage-Style Diamond Tufted Sofa<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Diamond tufting with its iconic diagonal pattern casts a traditional glow in the living room, but that doesn\u2019t mean it cannot blend well with more modern setups. It lends an air of sophistication and old-world charm no matter which room it adorns. The greatest advantage of using tufted sofas is their versatility. These aren\u2019t meant to be shunned to the corner \u2014 instead, make them the glamorous focal point of your room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112027\/diamond-tufted-sofa-in-vintage-style.jpg\" alt=\"Diamond tufted sofas in vintage style cast a traditional glow in the living room\" class=\"wp-image-34997\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112027\/diamond-tufted-sofa-in-vintage-style.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112027\/diamond-tufted-sofa-in-vintage-style-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112027\/diamond-tufted-sofa-in-vintage-style-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112027\/diamond-tufted-sofa-in-vintage-style-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A diamond tufted sofa provides interesting texture<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern And Minimal Grey Tufted Sofa<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This contemporary tufted sofa is the visual heart of the living room. With grey being one of the popular colour choices for the living room, a grey tufted sofa exudes unparalleled regal splendour. When paired with complementary colours like blue, white, or even gold, the space appears luxe and charming.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112039\/modern-and-minimal-gray-tufted-sofa.jpg\" alt=\"A modern and minimal gray tufted sofa is the visual heart of the living room\" class=\"wp-image-34999\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112039\/modern-and-minimal-gray-tufted-sofa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112039\/modern-and-minimal-gray-tufted-sofa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112039\/modern-and-minimal-gray-tufted-sofa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112039\/modern-and-minimal-gray-tufted-sofa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A grey tufted sofa to soften a modern living room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"End-to-end home interior design solutions for a stunning home\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180939\/end-to-end-home-interior-design-solutions-for-stunning-home.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Glamorously Large Tufted Sofa<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Furniture can be expensive but making smart choices with some of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">Design Cafe\u2019s<\/a> hacks will ensure that you don\u2019t burn a hole in your pocket. If you\u2019re going with a large tufted sofa in red velvet, you can pair it with cushions in various interesting prints and textures to add visual layers to the room. Dark colours are saturated and bold so create a balance in the room by keeping other furniture pieces light and few to not overwhelm the space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112032\/glamorously-large-tufted-sofa.jpg\" alt=\"A glamorous large tufted sofa in red velvet paired it with cushions\" class=\"wp-image-34998\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112032\/glamorously-large-tufted-sofa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112032\/glamorously-large-tufted-sofa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112032\/glamorously-large-tufted-sofa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112032\/glamorously-large-tufted-sofa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Complete the living room with a large tufted sofa<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Luxurious Chesterfield Sofa With Tufted Detail<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Synonymous with luxury, the chesterfield tufted sofa is a world in itself. With the opulent leather deep buttoning in a diamond pattern, low back and high arms, this classic can be found in the movies, decor showrooms and the dreams of every home decor enthusiast. This distinctive sofa style became popular in the 1700s and finds resonance in our homes even today. Something of a status symbol, the chesterfield tufted sofa is now available in various fabrics if leather is not your thing. Velvet or linen tufted sofas in shades of ruby and emerald are the most desirable.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112013\/chesterfield-sofa-with-tufted-details.jpg\" alt=\"A chesterfield sofa with tufted detail and opulent leather deep buttoning in a diamond pattern lends a luxurious look\" class=\"wp-image-34995\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112013\/chesterfield-sofa-with-tufted-details.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112013\/chesterfield-sofa-with-tufted-details-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112013\/chesterfield-sofa-with-tufted-details-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112013\/chesterfield-sofa-with-tufted-details-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>The chesterfield sofa is a classic for a reason<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Make A Statement With This Tan Tufted Sofa<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You could place a tan tufted sofa in any room, minus the embellishments and yet the room will look dressed nineteen to the dozen. You will be spoilt for choice; however, some points to keep in mind while choosing your tufted sofa are to check the frame, the legs, the cushioning and the suspension. Any wiggles, wobbles, sinks, squeaks and creaks should make you question the sofa\u2019s durability and comfort.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112047\/tan-tufted-sofa.jpg\" alt=\"A tan tufted sofa with colourful cushions blends well for a modern room\" class=\"wp-image-35000\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112047\/tan-tufted-sofa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112047\/tan-tufted-sofa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112047\/tan-tufted-sofa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112047\/tan-tufted-sofa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A tan tufted sofa is traditional at its best<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a free design consultation from design cafe\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/27144955\/get-free-design-consultation.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Trendy Tufted Armless Sofa<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>While tufted sofas are in vogue, an armless tufted futon serves as an intelligent space-saving alternative. They can be shifted from one room to the next, and be used as living room couches or guestroom cots \u2014 the flexibility of tufted futons is legendary.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112053\/trendy-tufted-armless-sofa.jpg\" alt=\"A tufted armless sofa serves as an intelligent space-saving alternative\" class=\"wp-image-35001\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112053\/trendy-tufted-armless-sofa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112053\/trendy-tufted-armless-sofa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112053\/trendy-tufted-armless-sofa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112053\/trendy-tufted-armless-sofa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Tufted futons for a compact and cosy space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tufted Daybeds<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>While cheap tufted sofas rule the roost, you could opt for tufted daybeds if you want more form and function without collecting too many heavy furniture pieces. These are best for <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/studio-apartment-interior-design-ideas\/\">studio apartments<\/a>, small spaces, work from home furniture, a home library or a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/reading-nook\/\">cosy reading nook<\/a>. Stack the tufted daybed against a wall and throw in some cushions to deny the discomfort of an absent backrest.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112104\/tufted-sofa-with-a-twist.jpg\" alt=\"A tufted sofa daybed is ideal for studio apartments or work from home furniture\" class=\"wp-image-35003\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112104\/tufted-sofa-with-a-twist.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112104\/tufted-sofa-with-a-twist-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112104\/tufted-sofa-with-a-twist-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112104\/tufted-sofa-with-a-twist-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A tufted daybed is a couch with a twist<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Velvet Tufted Sectional Sofa<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/sectional-sofa-design-ideas\/\">Sectional sofas<\/a> are finding a place in many <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/eclectic-interior-design-ideas\/\">eclectic homes<\/a>. The star of this segment is the velvet tufted sectional sofa that provides conversational style with its nuanced look. Bear in mind that tufted sofas are more challenging to maintain but they more than make up for it in style.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112111\/velvet-tufted-sectional-sofa.jpg\" alt=\"A velvet tufted sectional sofa in red provides conversational style with its nuanced look\" class=\"wp-image-35004\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112111\/velvet-tufted-sectional-sofa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112111\/velvet-tufted-sectional-sofa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112111\/velvet-tufted-sectional-sofa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112111\/velvet-tufted-sectional-sofa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Sink into the plushness of this tufted sofa<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Contemporary Tufted Sofa In Industrial Grey<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Channel tufting \u2014 quite a rage in the \u201980s \u2014 is trending amongst those seeking contemporary tufted sofa looks. This style uses long tufted channels to secure the cushioning. It doesn\u2019t have any buttons and creates clean, sleek lines that complement modern aesthetics proving that tufted sofas don\u2019t always have to be vintage.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112020\/contemporary-tufted-sofa-in-industrial-grey.jpg\" alt=\"A contemporary tufted sofa in grey complements modern aesthetics\" class=\"wp-image-34996\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112020\/contemporary-tufted-sofa-in-industrial-grey.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112020\/contemporary-tufted-sofa-in-industrial-grey-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112020\/contemporary-tufted-sofa-in-industrial-grey-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/10112020\/contemporary-tufted-sofa-in-industrial-grey-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Channel tufting sofa for an industrial-style home<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Tufted sofas in muted, traditional colours or deep, rich jewel tones create a beautiful interplay of textures and anchor the room in style and comfort. It is easy to achieve a modern-day glam look in your homes \u2014 simply place a tufted sofa against the backdrop of tastefully selected decor pieces, roll out a supple rug and voila! You are ready to throw a party.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\">\n                    +01\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+91\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06164015\/